WEBVTT

00:00:02.979 --> 00:00:09.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Kind and patient,
perfect in love,

00:00:09.645 --> 00:00:16.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Was Christ,
who came down from above.

00:00:16.104 --> 00:00:24.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He took care of our needs
With words and by deeds;

00:00:24.020 --> 00:00:31.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He gave of his time
and his love.

00:00:31.562 --> 00:00:38.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He would keep
the lowly in mind

00:00:38.479 --> 00:00:44.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
By healing the sick,
deaf, and blind.

00:00:44.895 --> 00:00:52.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
To his royal commission
he proved true

00:00:52.770 --> 00:01:01.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And willingly said:
“I want to.”

00:01:03.479 --> 00:01:10.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We now try
to follow his way

00:01:10.770 --> 00:01:17.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In all of our dealings
each day.

00:01:17.229 --> 00:01:25.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We are loving and kind
To all whom we find;

00:01:25.104 --> 00:01:32.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We help them
to learn and obey.

00:01:32.854 --> 00:01:39.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We respond
to friends when in need;

00:01:39.479 --> 00:01:45.979 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We love them
in word and in deed.

00:01:45.979 --> 00:01:53.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So if widows and orphans
should ask you,

00:01:53.895 --> 00:02:02.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Then readily say:
“I want to.”

